 :tx/rationale "Create task: AR-TEST: Comprehensive ambient reconciliation verification — proptest graph correctness + regression test + E2E script (INV-GUIDANCE-024, INV-BILATERAL-002, INV-STORE-014). BACKGROUND: The verification must cover all 3 components: graph engine, trace producer, concentration detector. Plus the specific regression that triggered this EPIC: TSV task creation not surfacing ACP overlap. APPROACH: (1) Proptest for spec_graph_neighbors: for any store with spec elements S and tasks T where T traces-to S, spec_graph_neighbors(store, [S.id]) contains T.entity (no false negatives). Converse: for any task T that does NOT trace to S, T.entity NOT in spec_graph_neighbors(store, [S.id]) (no false positives). (2) Unit test for IDF weighting: spec with 50 references produces lower score than spec with 2 references for the same hop distance. (3) REGRESSION TEST (the exact failure mode): create store with (a) ACP EPIC entity with :task/traces-to pointing to INV-INTERFACE-001 spec entity, (b) new TSV task entity also with :task/traces-to to INV-INTERFACE-001. Call spec_graph_neighbors(store, ['INV-INTERFACE-001']). Assert ACP EPIC entity is in results. This is the test that would have caught our failure. (4) Unit test for concentration detector: write 5 :recon/trace datoms with same :recon/trace-neighborhood 'INTERFACE'. Call spec_neighborhood_concentration(store, 20). Assert signal fires with trace_count=5. (5) E2E script scripts/e2e_ambient_reconciliation.sh with 12+ checks: (a) Init store. (b) Create spec element INV-TEST-RECON. (c) Create task-A tracing to INV-TEST-RECON. (d) Create task-B tracing to INV-TEST-RECON. (e) Verify task-B creation produced :recon/trace datom. (f) Verify trace contains task-A as neighbor. (g) Create 3 more tasks tracing to INV-TEST-RECON. (h) Run braid status. (i) Verify status output contains concentration warning. (j) Create task with NO spec refs → verify no :recon/trace produced. (k) Create task tracing to completely different spec → verify no concentration. (l) Performance: measure trace production time, assert <5ms. ACCEPTANCE: (A) Proptest: no false negatives or false positives for graph traversal (100 iterations). (B) Regression test passes (ACP surfaced for TSV). (C) Concentration detector fires at 3+ threshold. (D) E2E: 12+ checks all pass. (E) No existing tests regress. DEPENDS-ON: AR-4. FILE: crates/braid-kernel/src/guidance.rs (tests) + scripts/e2e_ambient_reconciliation.sh"
